description:
This is a market on whether whether the yield of the United States 10-Year Treasury Bond reaches 5.000% or more between October 24 and market close on November 8, 2022. 

If the yield of the US 10-Year T-Bond has crossed 5.000% or greater at any time between between October 24 and market close on November 8, 2022, this market will resolve to “Yes”. If the yield of the US 10-Year T-Bond does not reach 5.000% at any time between October 24 and market close on November 8, 2022, this market will resolve to “No”.  

The resolution source for this market will be investing.com's reporting found at https://www.investing.com/rates-bonds/u.s.-10-year-bond-yield-historical-data. The resolution will be based on the values listed in the column labelled “High” in rows titled by dates within this market's timeframe.
